<AbstractNarration>The proposal plans to connect SUNY-A to vBNS and Abilene via the NYSERNet Network for the following research and educational purposes:  electronic government funded by the NSF PACI program;  northeast regional climate modeling; interactive real-time regional air quality forecast and management system; real-time transmission of meteorological data; mesocale model and global analysis; network-based visualization of large-scale databases.</AbstractNarration>
